            <title><![CDATA[中共二十大中央委员和中纪委委员已选举产生]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/xxjpsgc007036_20221022_pepfn0a001.jpg?VersionId=wXXYmNRUUo0IFxVL09.2PoIAy7IjYVyj&amp;itok=_xRAW9VX" title="中共二十大闭幕会今天在京举行，大会已选举产生中央委员和中央纪律检查委员会名单。（新华社）" alt="中共二十大闭幕会今天在京举行，大会已选举产生中央委员和中央纪律检查委员会名单。（新华社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/xxjpsgc007036_20221022_pepfn0a001.jpg?VersionId=wXXYmNRUUo0IFxVL09.2PoIAy7IjYVyj&amp;itok=_xRAW9VX" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
